cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a novel scheme for generating large high-quality images using deep generative models. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also involves the use of tensor structures and super-resolution techniques, which are relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on three datasets, which is relevant to multimedia (cs.MM).
